name: It is not REEL (dam, artistly, forgspabghjekw, milkbread, ehonk)
name_original: It is not REEL (dam, artistly, forgspabghjekw, milkbread, ehonk)
description:
Travel through the deep sea with a close relative. Use your fishing rod to move through levels.

But something doesn't feel right...

Controls:

- W: Jump

- A, D: Move Left & Right

- Click: Grapple
